<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[الآيات الواردة في <span class="c2">«الفجور»</span>]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١- أَمْ نَجْعَلُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحاتِ كَالْمُفْسِدِينَ فِي الْأَرْضِ أَمْ نَجْعَلُ الْمُتَّقِينَ كَالْفُجَّارِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢- وَقالَ نُوحٌ رَبِّ لا تَذَرْ عَلَى الْأَرْضِ مِنَ الْكافِرِينَ دَيَّاراً <span class="c2">(٢٦)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إِنَّكَ إِنْ تَذَرْهُمْ يُضِلُّوا عِبادَكَ وَلا يَلِدُوا إِلَّا فاجِراً كَفَّاراً <span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣- لا أُقْسِمُ بِيَوْمِ الْقِيامَةِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلا أُقْسِمُ بِالنَّفْسِ اللَّوَّامَةِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَيَحْسَبُ الْإِنْسانُ أَلَّنْ نَجْمَعَ عِظامَهُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بَلى قادِرِينَ عَلى أَنْ نُسَوِّيَ بَنانَهُ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بَلْ يُرِيدُ الْإِنْسانُ لِيَفْجُرَ أَمامَهُ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>يَسْئَلُ أَيَّانَ يَوْمُ الْقِيامَةِ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٤- فَإِذا جاءَتِ الصَّاخَّةُ <span class="c2">(٣٣)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>يَوْمَ يَفِرُّ الْمَرْءُ مِنْ أَخِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٤)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَأُمِّهِ وَأَبِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَصاحِبَتِهِ وَبَنِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٦)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لِكُلِّ امْرِئٍ مِنْهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٧)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُسْفِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>ضاحِكَةٌ مُسْتَبْشِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٣٩)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْها غَبَرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>تَرْهَقُها قَتَرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أُولئِكَ هُمُ الْكَفَرَةُ الْفَجَرَةُ <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٥- إِنَّ الْأَبْرارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٍ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَإِنَّ الْفُجَّارَ لَفِي جَحِيمٍ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٦- كَلَّا إِنَّ كِتابَ الفُجَّارِ لَفِي سِجِّينٍ <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَما أَدْراكَ ما سِجِّينٌ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>كِتابٌ مَرْقُومٌ <span class="c2">(٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٦»</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>٧- وَالشَّمْسِ وَضُحاها <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>وَالْقَمَرِ إِذا تَلاها <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>وَالنَّهارِ إِذا جَلَّاها <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>وَاللَّيْلِ إِذا يَغْشاها <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>وَالسَّماءِ وَما بَناها <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>وَالْأَرْضِ وَما طَحاها <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>وَنَفْسٍ وَما سَوَّاها <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>فَأَلْهَمَها فُجُورَها وَتَقْواها <span class="c2">(٨)</span> <span class="c2">«٧»</span><a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
